    {
        "content": "<p>See <a href=\"#narrow/stream/229136-theory.3A-category.20theory/topic/lax.20morphism.20classifiers/near/224579928\">this reply</a> by Rune Haugseng for the more general case of lax functors of 2-categories (just specialise to the “single object” case).</p>",
